title: 95 Simple Ways to Overcome Stress from Unmet Expectations in Life with Christine Hassler
description:
"Whatever you're yearning for from out there, from someone else, is really something you're looking for inside yourself." - Christine Hassler
To read all the show notes and connect with those mentioned in the show, head on over to www.LewisHowes.com/95
